  "changelogHtml": "<h3 id=\"2.5.2\" data-text=\"Version 2.5.2\" tabindex=\"-1\">Version 2.5.2</h3>\n<p>June 21, 2023</p>\n<p><code translate=\"no\" dir=\"ltr\">androidx.room:room-*:2.5.2</code> is released. <a href=\"https://android.googlesource.com/platform/frameworks/support/+log/2f3269d9f8da6386519f59da82b374779e22c515..0c21d31673c507b0cddf8cf3b21235810f879a39/room\">Version 2.5.2 contains these commits.</a></p>\n<p><strong>Bug Fixes</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Fix an incompatibility issue with the kotlinx-metadata-jvm. (<a href=\"https://android-review.googlesource.com/#/q/29dfed77605e8f58a1acc6c452f4c70d5a386d5c\">386d5c</a>)</li>\n<li>Fix an issue that causes Room to throw an error when being used in a Robolectric test. (<a href=\"https://android-review.googlesource.com/#/q/05f5f7173f40b012dc58c773391ed72336f79bea\">f79bea</a>, <a href=\"https://issuetracker.google.com/issues/274924903\">b/274924903</a>)</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"version_251_3\" data-text=\"Version 2.5.1\" tabindex=\"-1\">Version 2.5.1</h2>",
